attacks.damage: Shuffle your hand into your deck. Draw a card for each card in your opponent's hand.
- Play this card as if it were a 40-HP Basic Colorless Pokemon. At any time during your turn, you may discard this card from play. This card can't retreat.
- Put a Basic Pokemon from your opponent's discard pile onto their Bench.
- Look at the top card of your deck. If that card is a Psychic Pokemon, put it in your hand. If it is not a Psychic Pokemon, put it on the bottom of your deck.
- Put your Mew ex in the Active Spot into your hand.
- During your opponent's next turn, all of your Pokemon take -10 damage from attacks from your opponent's Pokemon.
- During this turn, the Retreat Cost of your Active Pokemon is 2 less.
